FAQ_TITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Get Fit with Our Gym App
FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Everything you need to know about making the most of your workouts
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_1: What features does the app offer?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: Our app provides customized workout plans, exercise tutorials, progress tracking, and a community to connect with fellow fitness enthusiasts.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_2: How do I get started with the app?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: Simply download the app, create your profile, set your fitness goals, and start following the recommended workout routines.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_3: Can I track my progress over time?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: Yes, the app allows you to log your workouts, measure improvements in strength and endurance, and visualize your progress through charts and graphs.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_4: Is the app suitable for beginners?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: Absolutely! Our app caters to all fitness levels, offering beginner-friendly exercises and gradual progression to help you build a sustainable routine.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_5: How can I connect with the fitness community?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: The app has a social component where you can join groups, share your achievements, and get motivation and support from like-minded individuals.

PLACEHOLDER_FAQ_TITLE: Frequently Asked Questions About Our Gym App
ACCORDION_QUESTION_1: What features does the gym app offer?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: Our gym app provides a comprehensive suite of tools to enhance your fitness journey. Track your workouts, log meals, connect with trainers, access workout plans, and monitor your progress all in one convenient place.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_2: Is the app suitable for beginners?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: Absolutely! The app caters to all fitness levels, from novices to seasoned athletes. It offers beginner-friendly programs, exercise demonstrations, and personalized guidance to help you kickstart your fitness routine.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_3: Can I connect with a personal trainer through the app?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: Yes, our app allows you to connect with certified personal trainers who can provide tailored workout plans, nutrition advice, and virtual coaching sessions to keep you motivated and on track.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_4: How does the app track my progress?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: The app utilizes advanced algorithms to track your progress based on the data you input, such as workout logs, body measurements, and fitness goals. This allows you to visualize your achievements and identify areas for improvement.
